Class Set

  • java.lang.Object
    • jp.go.aist.six.oval.model.definitions.Set
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OvalObject

    public class Set
extends Object
implements OvalObject
    The Set enables complex objects to be described. It is a recursive element in that each set element can contain additional set elements as children.
